        public RenderParameters(java.lang.String target,
                        IModulePageLayouter.IRenderingLayout layout,
                        int level,
                        int localLevel,
                        java.lang.CharSequence idAttrib,
                        IWorkItem workItem,
                        ILocalId currentDocumentId)
        Parameters:
        target - target of render (e.g. HTML, PDF, ...)
        layout - layout (not null)
        level - work item's structural level
        localLevel - local (inside closest heading) work item's structural level (has no meaning for headings)
        idAttrib - id attribute from enclosing element or null if none specified
        workItem - work item to render, null in call to renderWorkItemTemplate, otherwise cannot be null
